<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039141" n="1"/>
  <opener><salute>Viros Juvenes Eruditissimos <rs key="pers_DE-588-122682769" type="person">F. L. Spr<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>nglinum</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-1168632560" type="person">S. Risoldum</rs>
    <lb/>plurimum salvere jubet <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">NB.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quamvis nullus dubitem, Amici charissimi, Vos su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o cum desiderio Literas <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me expectare, et
  <lb/>proinde silentium meum tam diuturnum non posse non Vobis admodum displicere, facile tamen
  <lb/>credo, vos non eo animo esse, ut ob istam quam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>isi in scribendo moram statim credatis, me
  <lb/>charissima vestra nomina et tot benevolenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> argumenta mihi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Vobis per breve hoc tempus,
  <lb/>quo vestra usus sum conversatione, exhibita tam cito oblivioni tradidisse; et hinc etiam est,
  <lb/>quod veniam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vobis me haud difficulter impetraturum sperem. Varia negotia et visita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiones, quibus me defungi oportuit, hactenus scriptionem impediverunt, nunc autem mihi
  <lb/>redditus haud quiescendum esse duxi, antequam promissa vobis exsolverim. Primum autem
  <lb/>et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipuum quod vobis dicendum habeo, est ut vos rogem, ut amicitiam, qua me dignari
  <lb/>voluistis, mihi porro conservetis integram; ea certe ab initio statim multum apud me valuit,
  <lb/>et su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a voluptas, quam ex colloquiis vestris hausi, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim ex ultimo, quo mutuum nobis
  <lb/>invicem vale diximus, causa fuit, ut vos sine maximo dolore deserere non potuerim. I<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>otus,
  <lb/>sane h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>si ad omnia vota vestra, quibus me abeuntem comitati estis, et lachr<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>jamjam eruptionem minabantur, vobis pro merito respondere dignasque gratias agere mihi
  <lb/>non permiserunt. Sensi profecto ex eo demum tempore, et adhuc sentio, quid sit <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> sinceris dis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jungi amicis; tristiti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> me etiamnum totum concederem, nisi animum adderet spes vos brevi
  <lb/>tempore <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> videndi. Agite igitur et promissa vestra implete; Te pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue, amicissime
  <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-122682769" type="person">Sprüngline</rs>, sub finem proximi mensis <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> expecto, ego me domi futurum spero <date>28. ejus
    <lb/>mensis</date>, quod si igitur metuas, ne adventus meus nimis sero contingat, rogo ut mihi tempus
  <lb/>abitus tui significes, ut si opus sit iter meum accelerare queam. Te quoque, <rs key="pers_DE-588-1168632560" type="person">Risolde</rs> opti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me, vere proximo <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> transiturum, meque ibidem, ut promisisti, salutaturum<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>esse confido. Venite igitur, amici charissimi, et me arctiori vinculo vobis conjun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gite, simulque <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ab amico sperari possunt, officiorum genera expectate.
  <lb/>Interim Valete quam optime una cum <rs type="person">Sutermeistero</rs> vestro, cui meo nomine plurimam nun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiare salutem rogo ne dedignemini.</p>
  <closer><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> <date when="1710-07-15">15. <abbr>Jul.</abbr> 1710.</date> <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place"><hi rend="u">Genevam</hi></rs></dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Literas, si quas ad me scribere vobis placuerit, date <rs key="pers_DE-588-1132220874" type="person">Raillardo</rs>, qui eas suis includere
  <lb/>non cessabit.</p>
</postscript>
</div>
